    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 assessment plan. Validation evidence demonstrates sufficient model credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The bound requirement (https://uofa.net/morrison/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2) and claim (https://uofa.net/morrison/claim/cpb-hemolysis-worst-case) together define the intended-use scope for this assessment. Decision: Accepted for regulatory submission supporting 510(k) predicate comparison.",
